NOW, LOOK, ANNABELLE.
THAT DOLL TALKED TO ME.

18:54.008 --> 18:57.126
THAT DOLL SAID THINGS
NO DOLL SHOULD SAY.

18:57.219 --> 18:59.381
I HAD TO GET RID OF IT.

18:59.472 --> 19:01.634
YOU'VE BECOME
A STRANGER TO ME, ERICH,

19:01.724 --> 19:03.886
A SICK,
NEUROTIC STRANGER.

19:03.976 --> 19:07.344
YOU'RE FILLED WITH BLIND,
UNREASONABLE HATE.

19:07.438 --> 19:09.475
YOU BETTER SEE
A GOOD PSYCHIATRIST.

19:16.155 --> 19:18.317
I COULDN'T
HAVE IMAGINED IT.

19:18.407 --> 19:21.195
TELL HIM YOU TRIED
TO KILL A DOLL.

19:21.285 --> 19:23.151
I COULDN'T...

19:23.245 --> 19:25.828
I COULDN'T.

19:25.915 --> 19:32.082
WHAT DID YOU DO
WITH IT?

19:32.171 --> 19:34.253
I'LL GIVE IT BACK.

19:34.340 --> 19:38.083
I'LL GIVE IT BACK
TO CHRISTIE.

19:38.177 --> 19:41.511
WILL THAT
SOLVE THINGS?

19:41.597 --> 19:43.838
I DON'T KNOW, ERICH.

20:09.625 --> 20:11.866
[clatters]

20:29.645 --> 20:31.727
<i>MY NAME IS TALKY TINA,</i>

20:31.814 --> 20:34.476
<i>AND I DON'T
FORGIVE YOU.</i>

20:34.567 --> 20:36.228
[whispering]
SHUT UP.

20:36.277 --> 20:37.688
PLEASE, SHUT UP.

21:08.434 --> 21:11.017
TINA.

21:11.103 --> 21:12.844
TINA!

21:12.938 --> 21:14.394
OH, TINA.

21:23.449 --> 21:26.032
<i>[electric whirring]</i>

21:35.127 --> 21:37.084
<i>[whirring continues]</i>

21:49.475 --> 21:51.637
<i>[whirring sfvps]</i>

21:51.727 --> 21:54.640
WHAT IS IT?

21:54.730 --> 22:00.146
[gulps]
<i>I</i> HEARD SOMETHING.

22:00.236 --> 22:01.772
ERICH, I DON'T
HEAR ANYTHING.

22:06.075 --> 22:07.156
NO, STAY THERE.

22:16.085 --> 22:18.497
<i>[whirring resumes]</i>

22:30.307 --> 22:34.346
<i>[whirring grows faint]</i>

22:49.869 --> 22:51.451
<i>[whirring sfvps]</i>

23:10.556 --> 23:12.888
<i>[whirring resumes]</i>

23:18.856 --> 23:20.563
<i>[whirring continues]</i>

23:43.088 --> 23:45.250
[screaming]
ERICH!

23:50.220 --> 23:52.507
ERICH.

23:52.598 --> 23:56.842
<i>MY NAME IS
TALKY TINA...</i>

23:56.936 --> 24:00.349
<i>AND YOU'D BETTER
BE NICE TO ME.</i>

24:03.567 --> 24:06.685
<i>(narrator) OF COURSE, WE ALL
KNOW DOLLS CAN'T REALLY TALK,</i>

24:06.779 --> 24:09.362
<i>AND THEY CERTAINLY
CAN'T COMMIT MURDER.</i>

24:09.448 --> 24:11.280
<i>BUT TO A CHILD</i>

24:11.367 --> 24:13.608
<i>CAUGHT IN THE MIDDLE
OF TURMOIL AND CONFLICT,</i>

24:13.702 --> 24:15.204
<i>A DOLL CAN BECOME
MANY THINGS.'</i>

24:15.287 --> 24:18.200
<i>FRIEND, DEFENDER, GUARDIAN.</i>

24:18.290 --> 24:20.452
<i>ESPECIALLYA DOLL
LIKE TALKY TINA,</i>

24:20.542 --> 24:23.204
<i>WHO DID TALK
AND DID COMMIT MURDER--</i>

24:23.295 --> 24:26.333
<i>IN THE MISTY REGION
OF THE TWILIGHT ZONE.</i>

24:31.387 --> 24:33.378
<i>(male presenter)
AND NOW MR. SERLING.</i>

24:33.472 --> 24:36.555
NEXT ON TI/V/L/GHTZONE, A
JOURNEY INTO A FUTURE MOMENT,

24:36.642 --> 24:39.555
A NIGHTMARISH,
FRIGHTENING MOMENT IN TIME,

24:39.645 --> 24:41.477
WHEN MAN SITS
IN HIS OWN RUBBLE

24:41.522 --> 24:44.230
AND SURVEYS THE LEGACY
HE'S LEFT TO HIMSELF.

24:44.316 --> 24:46.398
JAMES COBURN
AND JOHN ANDERSON

24:46.485 --> 24:49.227
STAR IN
"THE OLD MAN IN THE CAVE."

